org.cpsolver.studentsct.online

Class OnlineConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.context.AbstractClassWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Config.ConfigContext>
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.model.Config
        • org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.OnlineConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CanHoldContext, CanInheritContext<Request,Enrollment,Config.ConfigContext>, HasAssignmentContext<Request,Enrollment,Config.ConfigContext>

    public class OnlineConfig
extends Config
    An online configuration. A simple extension of the Config class that allows to set the current configuration enrollment. This class is particularly useful when a model containing only the given student is constructed (to provide him/her with a schedule or suggestions).
